{"tid":1580121,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金義聖見721傷者","createTime":"2019-09-19T02:07:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-19T03:35:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"56719de3effe70c157da9dbbed4b466f2c5c3c83","tid":1580121,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:07:40.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190919/20770706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F20770706&d=gqDWnnaI%2FM4dwC7GJUFj5QjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=1bdccb59\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190919%2F20770706&h=3ab88356\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20190919/20770706</a><br />\n<br />\n金義聖見721傷者<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190919/large/1568808483_dc09.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190919%2Flarge%2F1568808483_dc09.jpg&h=1587ce21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金義聖昨日與立法會議員見面。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n韓片《屍殺列車》的53歲男星金義聖日前孖韓國MBC新聞節目《探查企劃Straight》攝製隊來港，實地採訪香港的示威情況。前晚金義聖到理工大學拍攝短片，接受MBC新聞節目《News Desk》採訪，並透露與「721元朗站無差別打市民」的傷者見面：「我跟受害者見面，不只身體受傷，他們亦遭受嚴重的精神創傷。」他亦提到「警黑合作」，指香港市民因是次襲擊而完全失去對警察的信任。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20190919/large/1568808483_4434.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20190919%2Flarge%2F1568808483_4434.jpg&h=9479a720&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金義聖（左）接受MBC新聞節目《News Desk》的採訪時表示與元朗721的傷者見面。<br />\n<br />\n另外，金義聖昨日與本港立法會議員譚文豪、林卓廷和許智峯見面，譚文豪和林卓廷都有在facebook上載與金義聖的合照，而金義聖傍晚再到太子站進行拍攝，有網民留言指他可以拍太子版《廝殺列車》。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：施洛冰 <br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n是非人物冇人肯合作 山口真帆寫真稱冠現身谷盡<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\nRihanna兩度遲到激嬲韓媒"},{"pid":"526a5b5e021992c5b119defdf6b7d5f9b7ad912e","tid":1580121,"uid":2607,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:08:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人地韓星都做得好過你成個港共政權"},{"pid":"4aff7599633108572cd1f6ab1b5e1c6c2fc2045c","tid":1580121,"uid":58958,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:14:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />感動感謝"},{"pid":"ad5787267dc579ebc97a5d118b8672fe23cefd7d","tid":1580121,"uid":78184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:19:31.000Z","msg":"Thank you"},{"pid":"134b182c6ea70d58b89c0855b6c2dc8f7311e40a","tid":1580121,"uid":268519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:26:30.000Z","msg":"佢尋晚都去左太子站<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74928c32cdd9cb66cb06bbf0affcc19a0f3e1773","tid":1580121,"uid":29311,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:55:58.000Z","msg":"佢真係好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一路keep住關注 唔止祈禱<br />\n仲搞campaign 又親身嚟香港<br />\n香港啲奶共偽人知唔知醜"},{"pid":"6c3c2be1d6a0b70b8b9bc3bf0158372f0888ce5a","tid":1580121,"uid":37146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T02:58:17.000Z","msg":"點解會咁既？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6afc66df54000d373dfd3150c721b7d48929bf34","tid":1580121,"uid":33077,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:18:22.000Z","msg":"佢都經歷過光洲事件 就似我地咁<br />\n明白民主自由真係唔可以放棄，一放棄就咩都無晒"},{"pid":"7e7786516eaddfe750cfacafa2ed001fb8d6dad6","tid":1580121,"uid":247840,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T03:19:56.000Z","msg":"佢似香港特首 多過香港對上4條廢物"},{"pid":"93baa7bbd256b784fa975e8b7c674515f7567d9d","tid":1580121,"uid":71382,"like":0,"di